snippet.title: Project Zero Deaths Trailer
snippet.description:
Project Zero Deaths is a hectic physics-based F2P online multiplayer platform shooter. 

Jump into frantic battles in dynamic maps, solo or with friends, to fight in varied wild game modes! 

Choose between different characters with unique skills and customize them and their weapons to your own playstyle!

GET IT NOW!
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.detis.pzd&referrer=utm_source%3Dsite%26utm_medium%3Ddownload-link
Apple App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/project-zero-deaths/id1459390287
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/10...

JOIN THE COMMUNITY ON DISCORD:
https://discord.gg/XEVtPp4
